title: Faces off the Field: Antonio Soriano, senior RB/DB, Eastside...
text:
What’s your favorite football memory from high school?
Just recently we played East Austin College Prep. It was said to be a rivalry game, but I knew it wasn’t, and beating them 50-7 just proved that it wasn’t.
